value: Resident, flat open country: S Ethiopia, NW Somalia - N Tanzania; S Angola, Namibia - S Mozambique, South Africa (not south and east).

flat arid, mostly open country, usually with a short herb layer, e.g.grassland, karoo, bushveld, thornveld, scrubland & savanna;also floodplains, duneland, & wheat fields and firebeaks;generally below 2000m

subcat_descr: Bill length (sex unknown) - Nares to tip
